@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xqevat(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = v0
    v0 = 0.72
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.19 - v2 + 0.71) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.44)) + (0.03 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.79)))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.62 / (tmp + 0.37 + v2 + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
